<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;*SCP-CN-1274-03&nbsp;”萨布丽娜“</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
